These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
2 different pets are kept: hamster, rabbit
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, ship
1. the person driving the roller is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| Pet          | rabbit | hamster    |
| Hobby         | chess   | board-games |
| Transport   | roller  | ship      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, red
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, metal
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile
1. the person who likes red is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the fan of blues##5
3. the fan of metal is not to the right of the fan of blues##8
4. the person driving the boat is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Color    | blood-red        | red    |
| Hobby       | filmmaking         | woodworking |
| Music-Genre         | metal | blues   |
| Transport   | boat               | snowmobile  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, thriller
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, peach
There are 2 different favourite colors: turquise, red
1. the person eating asparagus is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating peach is not to the right of the person who likes red##8
3. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | thriller |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | metal    |
| Food   | asparagus | peach |
| Color           | turquise        | red   |

