2. the mexican is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the fan of metal is not the person watching drama movies##6
4. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the fan of metal##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama      | time-travel |
| Nationality   | mexican    | pakistani   |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate | almond-milk     |
| Music-Genre     | salsa | metal  |

